item.title: Everytime I tele to pc i freeze?
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

[quote=“48 Jumps, post:2, topic:274876”]The reason you freeze when you teleport to Pest Control, is one of three things.

  1. Your Client doesn’t have the Map. (If you are using an old client this is 9/10 the problem).

  2. Your 'toX toY' method is messed up.

  3. You entered the Coordinates you want the Pest Control tele, to tele you to are way off.

If it’s not either of these things, or you can’t tell PM me.

If I left some things out I’m sorry, I’m sure I left at least 5+ more out. :([/quote]Those reasons (Most likely), or, post the code you’re using and I’ll try to help you out.
